<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-214] Quota commands deprecated and needs to be fixed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-214</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since Lustre 2.4.0, lfs quotaon and quotaoff are deprecated. Although the deprecation is well noted in the manual, this should be added to section 33.1.3 &quot;lfs options&quot; after quotaon and quotaoff are listed as options and, probably, the example in 33.1.4 should not use quotaon and quotaoff.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
